<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Creative Glass Card</title>
    <style>
        /* 1. Setup the Background */
        body {
            margin: 0;
            height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            background: linear-gradient(45deg, #ee7752, #e73c7e, #23a6d5, #23d5ab);
            background-size: 400% 400%;
            animation: gradientBG 15s ease infinite;
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
        }

        @keyframes gradientBG {
            0% { background-position: 0% 50%; }
            50% { background-position: 100% 50%; }
            100% { background-position: 0% 50%; }
        }

        /* 2. The Glass Card */
        .card {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
            backdrop-filter: blur(15px); /* This creates the glass effect */
            border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
            padding: 2rem;
            width: 300px;
            border-radius: 20px;
            text-align: center;
            color: white;
            box-shadow: 0 8px 32px 0 rgba(31, 38, 135, 0.37);
            transition: transform 0.3s ease;
        }

        /* 3. Hover Animation */
        .card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-10px);
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
        }

        .profile-img {
            width: 100px;
            height: 100px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            background: #fff;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
            border: 3px solid #fff;
        }

        h2 { margin: 10px 0; letter-spacing: 1px; }

        p { font-size: 0.9rem; opacity: 0.8; line-height: 1.5; }

        .btn {
            margin-top: 20px;
            padding: 10px 25px;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 25px;
            background: #fff;
            color: #e73c7e;
            font-weight: bold;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: 0.3s;
        }

        .btn:hover {
            background: #333;
            color: #fff;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <div class="card">
        <div style="display: flex; justify-content: center;">
            <div class="profile-img">
                <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="#e73c7e" style="padding: 15px;"><path d="M12 12c2.21 0 4-1.79 4-4s-1.79-4-4-4-4 1.79-4 4 1.79 4 4 4zm0 2c-2.67 0-8 1.34-8 4v2h16v-2c0-2.66-5.33-4-8-4z"/></svg>
            </div>
        </div>
        <h2>Creative Dev</h2>
        <p>Day 2: Mastering the art of CSS Glassmorphism and animated gradients.</p>
        <button class="btn">View Portfolio</button>
    </div>

</body>
</html>
